sequenceDiagram
actor User
participant Browser
participant DjangoView as Django View (full_tree_interactive_view)
participant DjangoAPI as Django API (full_tree_data_graphviz)
participant TreeService as Tree Building Logic
participant GraphRenderer as Graph Rendering (Backend)
participant FrontendJS as D3 Frontend

User->>Browser: Opens "interactive tree" page
Browser->>DjangoView: GET /drzewo/full-tree-interactive/

DjangoView->>Browser: HTML + JS + initial form

Browser->>FrontendJS: Initialize application (main.js)
FrontendJS->>DjangoAPI: Fetch tree data (GET /full-tree-data/)

DjangoAPI->>TreeService: Build layers and edges
TreeService->>TreeService: Traverse models, compute structure
TreeService->>GraphRenderer: Render graph (Graphviz)
GraphRenderer-->>DjangoAPI: Graph + metadata

DjangoAPI-->>FrontendJS: JSON (nodes, links, years, childrenDict)

FrontendJS->>FrontendJS: Build internal state
FrontendJS->>FrontendJS: Render graph using D3

User->>FrontendJS: Interacts (filters / color / view modes)
FrontendJS->>FrontendJS: Update visualization dynamically